{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Game God of War Akan Mengeksplor Legenda Mesir Atau Maya: Kenapa Tidak India Saja?","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">God of War adalah sebuah <em>franchise</em> penting untuk Sony dan platform PlayStation mereka. Game action ini lahir di era PlayStation 2 dan menjadi game hits yang popularitasnya tetap tinggi bertahun-tahun kemudian. Dengan karakter sentral yang tetap sama sejak awal, yaitu Kratos, game God of War meraih kesuksesan di setiap rilisannya (kecuali di versi terakhir “God of War: Ascension” yang secara penjualan ternyata tidak begitu memuaskan).</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40622\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40622\" data-attachment-id=\"40622\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/god-of-war-iii-remastered_20150409214116/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;PlayStation(R)4&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;God of War\\u00ae III Remastered_20150409214116&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1428615675&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;God of War\\u00ae III Remastered_20150409214116&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kratos The Spartan. Sumber gambar: technobuffalo.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kratos The Spartan. Sumber gambar: technobuffalo.com&lt;br /&gt;\nKratos The Spartan. Sumber gambar: technobuffalo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40622\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-12.jpg\" alt=\"Kratos The Spartan. Sumber gambar: technobuffalo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40622\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kratos The Spartan. Sumber gambar: technobuffalo.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dengan berlatar belakang konflik di dunia mitologi Yunani klasik, God of War membuat kisah versi mereka sendiri dari latar belakang dewa-dewa Yunani yang sudah dikenal luas oleh dunia. Dewa-dewa seperti Zeus, Ares dan Athena muncul di game God of War dalam jalinan kisah yang diciptakan oleh team Santa Monica Studio; studio bawahan Sony selain Naughty Dog (yang juga menciptakan game fenomenal lainnya “<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-uncharted-lost-legacy-meneruskan-tradisi-uncharted%C2%AD%C2%AD/\">Uncharted</a>” series).</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40631\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40631\" data-attachment-id=\"40631\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/9-99/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/9-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kratos adu jotos dengan Dewa Zeus dari Olympus. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kratos adu jotos dengan Dewa Zeus dari Olympus. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/9-6.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/9-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40631\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/9-6.jpg\" alt=\"Kratos adu jotos dengan Dewa Zeus dari Olympus. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40631\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kratos adu jotos dengan Dewa Zeus dari Olympus. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sejak semula God of War memang fokus pada mitologi dewa-dewa Olympus. Dengan pintar team Santa Monica Studio (saat itu dipimpin oleh David Jaffe yang juga dianggap sebagai bapak/kreator game God of War ini) memasukkan karakter fiksi ciptaan mereka Kratos, seorang Spartan, ke dalam kisah mitologi Yunani. Hasilnya memang baik sekali. Dengan total penjualan melewati angka 21 juta unit menjadikan serial game ini andalan untuk platform Sony. Beberapa seri buku komik dan novel bertema God of War juga pernah terbit. Dan walaupun masih tetap berupa wacana namun film live action God of War tetap menjadi gosip hot di dunia gaming hingga kini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40610\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40610\" data-attachment-id=\"40610\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/2-220/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sosok dibalik lahirnya God of War. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sosok dibalik lahirnya God of War. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-25.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40610\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-25.jpg\" alt=\"Sosok dibalik lahirnya God of War. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40610\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sosok dibalik lahirnya God of War. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Game terkini dari <em>franchise</em> God of War direncanakan rilis tahun ini <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menanti-deretan-video-games-terbaik-yang-rilis-2017-2018/\">https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menanti-deretan-video-games-terbaik-yang-rilis-2017-2018/</a> dan akan menawarkan sesuatu yang baru, yaitu perubahan mitologi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40607\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40607\" data-attachment-id=\"40607\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/1-279/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"God of War PS4 tidak lagi soal dewa dewi Yunani. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;God of War PS4 tidak lagi soal dewa dewi Yunani. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-25.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40607\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-25.jpg\" alt=\"God of War PS4 tidak lagi soal dewa dewi Yunani. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40607\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">God of War PS4 tidak lagi soal dewa dewi Yunani. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jika seluruh game God of War sebelumnya merupakan adaptasi kisah para dewa Yunani maka di game terkini God of War ini mitologi Yunani akan ditinggalkan. Tokoh utama masih berupa Kratos, dan kini dia berada dalam mitologi Norse alias Norwegia.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40637\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40637\" data-attachment-id=\"40637\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/11-66/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/11-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tetap penuh dengan makhluk mitologi dunia. Kali ini dari Norwegia. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tetap penuh dengan makhluk mitologi dunia. Kali ini dari Norwegia. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/11-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/11-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40637\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/11-4.jpg\" alt=\"Tetap penuh dengan makhluk mitologi dunia. Kali ini dari Norwegia. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40637\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tetap penuh dengan makhluk mitologi dunia. Kali ini dari Norwegia. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mitologi Norwegia memang tidak kalah seru dengan Yunani. Dewa dan kejadian-kejadian dalam mitologi Norwegia cukup dikenal oleh dunia <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mitologi-ragnarok-mulai-dari-komik-marvel-hingga-game-online-rpg-korea/\">https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mitologi-ragnarok-mulai-dari-komik-marvel-hingga-game-online-rpg-korea/</a> sehingga mungkin karena alasan itulah team Santa Monica Studio memutuskan untuk membawa Kratos ‘mengacau’ dunia dewa Odin setelah sebelumnya meluluh-lantakkan dunia dewa Zeus.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40634\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40634\" data-attachment-id=\"40634\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/10-81/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/10-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gameplay baru. Mitologi baru. Sumber gambar: hdwallpapers.in\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gameplay baru. Mitologi baru. Sumber gambar: hdwallpapers.in&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/10-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/10-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40634\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/10-5.jpg\" alt=\"Gameplay baru. Mitologi baru. Sumber gambar: hdwallpapers.in\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40634\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gameplay baru. Mitologi baru. Sumber gambar: hdwallpapers.in</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Walau game terkini God of War itu belum resmi rilis di pasaran, namun trailernya sudah beredar lama di YouTube dan menghidupkan <em>‘hype’</em> akan God of War secara konstan. Aksi Kratos, yang kini memiliki seorang putra, di dunia mitologi Norse terasa fresh dan baru setelah sebelumnya penuh dengan referensi mitologi Yunani.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40625\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40625\" data-attachment-id=\"40625\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/7-149/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/7-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kratos dan putranya. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/playstationKratos dan putranya. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/playstation\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kratos dan putranya. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/playstation&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/7-9.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/7-9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40625\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/7-9.jpg\" alt=\"Kratos dan putranya. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/playstation\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40625\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kratos dan putranya. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/playstation</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi ada info menarik yang muncul langsung dari Cory Barlog, sutradara game God of Wars PS4 saat di wawancarai majalah “Game Informer”. Yaitu soal kemungkinan lokasi/mitologi yang digunakan untuk game God of War berikutnya, yakni antara Mesir ataupun Maya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40616\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40616\" data-attachment-id=\"40616\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/4-235/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cory Barlog. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cory Barlog. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-25.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40616\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-25.jpg\" alt=\"Cory Barlog. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40616\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cory Barlog. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cliff Bleszinski, kreator game <em>franchise</em> populer lainnya “Gears of War”, mengomentari informasi itu melalui akun Twitter-nya sambil me-mention Barlog dengan mengatakan kalau ide tersebut adalah ide bagus untuk kesinambungan God of War. Di dalam wawancara Barlog juga menyatakan kalau mereka (team Santa Monica Studio) mencoba hal-hal baru agar God of War tidak terjebak dalam monotonitas game-game sebelumnya, dan salah satu cara yang mereka lakukan serta pertimbangkan adalah dengan mengekspansi mitologi yang digunakan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40619\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40619\" data-attachment-id=\"40619\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/5-237/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-23.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Arah selanjutnya dari God of War? Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Arah selanjutnya dari God of War? Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-23.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-23.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40619\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-23.jpg\" alt=\"Arah selanjutnya dari God of War? Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40619\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Arah selanjutnya dari God of War? Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iseng, saya mencoba ikutan nimbrung di Tweet tersebut dengan mengatakan “seharusnya mereka mengeksplorasi mitologi India, karena Mahabharata adalah situasi epik peperangan yang cocok dengan atmosfir God of War selama ini”.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40613\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40613\" data-attachment-id=\"40613\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/3-244/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Nimbrung di tweet game developers hehehe. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Nimbrung di tweet game developers hehehe. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-25.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40613\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-25.jpg\" alt=\"Nimbrung di tweet game developers hehehe. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40613\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nimbrung di tweet game developers hehehe. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/therealcliffyb</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mitologi dewa-dewa India tidak lepas dari konflik dan peperangan sehingga jika dikelola secara tepat akan jadi sebuah skenario game God of War yang tidak akan kalah epik dibandingkan seri-seri sebelumnya. Bayangan saja kalau Kratos ada di dalam situasi Mahabharata! Siapa yang akan berurusan dengan dia? Apakah Khrisna? Ghatotkacha? Tentu bakal seru banget ‘kan?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40628\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-40628\" data-attachment-id=\"40628\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-god-war-akan-mengeksplor-legenda-mesir-atau-maya-kenapa-tidak-india-saja/attachment/8-118/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/8-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Salah satu ilustrasi Mahabharata. Sumber gambar: indiaopines.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Salah satu ilustrasi Mahabharata. Sumber gambar: indiaopines.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/8-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/8-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40628\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/8-7.jpg\" alt=\"Salah satu ilustrasi Mahabharata. Sumber gambar: indiaopines.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-40628\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salah satu ilustrasi Mahabharata. Sumber gambar: indiaopines.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dan tidak saya sangka, Tweet saya itu direspon oleh Cory Barlog.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Memang bukan hal istimewa sih, karena Barlog tidak berkomentar akan idea tersebut dan hanya memberi ‘like’. Tapi saya cukup puas karena setidaknya saya tahu kalau ide mitologi India bukan sesuatu yang mustahil untuk berada dalam <em>lore</em> game God of War menurut sutradara game God of War sendiri. Walaupun mungkin akan sedikit sulit karena mitologi India juga berkaitan erat dengan agama Hindu serta kepercayaan agamis yang dianut banyak pemeluknya. Merecoki sesuatu elemen agama dapat menimbulkan hal-hal yang bikin rumit situasi.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menurut bro sis sendiri, apakah ada mitologi dewa-dewi lain yang cocok dimasukkan ke dalam game God of War? Bisa kasi pendapatnya di bagian komen.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a6f95cf3-bc96-5ae6-a3ff-e0a2e3b01614"}}}